{"tid":449101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝一早就屌尻條癈二老","createTime":"2017-10-27T01:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T02:01:55.000Z","uid":102680,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"531825d38a516d32e3ba46c1b4aed730bf02eb78","tid":449101,"uid":102680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:35:38.000Z","msg":"話説今朝等巴士時，條人龍排撚到九里叫咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我排第2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 車一到有條癈老想打尻我尖，我即場大撚大聲屌柒佢，阿叔你訓撚醒未呀！打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後面咁撚多人排隊，排隊啦晨早流流博屌都on撚尻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢就真系走撚返去排隊，但後面D撚樣就若無其事咁，俾人打尖都唔撚敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c4062ee4d4f205e7c6cb4e6b8c9f3a7407a010","tid":449101,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01e05fc6e9bbbf40dbe52104dbe28e72978b0672","tid":449101,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:40:46.000Z","msg":"香港人的確好撚廢<br />\n次次得我出聲屌9人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個都淆撚哂底咁"},{"pid":"d9764a5a7b392a112ab5a38d483c04c356aae3e4","tid":449101,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T01:42:28.000Z","msg":"啲廢老好撚鐘意排撚晒野企隊頭隔離睇個車站牌<br />\n架車一到就好撚自然咁行埋黎上車"},{"pid":"e8b9b0c1ba08b0927d06bc04e7175fd5aa8ac41c","tid":449101,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:00:53.000Z","msg":"唉&hellip;有次係惠康串鳩個阿叔，佢拖住個細<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，間惠康地方細，收銀得兩格<br />\n所以排隊時就一條隊，邊邊搞掂去邊邊<br />\n咁阿叔見到得一條隊，就拖住個細路行左去冇人企過邊，仲同個細路講：依邊冇人排wo<br />\n<br />\n我又剛剛收工攰到仆街就忍唔住串鳩佢<br />\n話：阿生你咪以為自己好醒啦，條隊一開二架<br />\n<br />\n之後佢細路望下佢老豆，又望下我<br />\n<br />\n不過佢都係冇排隊，只係企到我比左錢之後就插返入隊<br />\n<br />\n後面啲人又冇出聲，我就由鳩佢"},{"pid":"074efe184f22b6747c1df9a264a2c9249f2b12d7","tid":449101,"uid":102680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T02:01:55.000Z","msg":"晨撚早屌佢一撚即刻精神爽利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}